  "body": "### Description of Issue\r\n\r\nSending a raw signed transaction via https://mycrypto.com/pushTx the prompt does not display the decimals properly for some tokens.\r\n\r\n![rect880-9](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1658405/80043867-275ca300-8503-11ea-9a28-975d248de173.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### What exactly were you doing when you encountered this issue?\r\n\r\nSending a raw signed transaction for a USDC transfer.\r\n\r\nThat token has 6 decimals as opposed to the usual 18: https://etherscan.io/address/0xa0b86991c6218b36c1d19d4a2e9eb0ce3606eb48#readProxyContract\r\n\r\n.. so I assume there must be some UI error that does not take into account the decimals of the token.\r\n",
